      "table_notes": [
        "Based on 6,262 franchised stores (of 6,699 operating at year end). 437 excluded: 256 incomplete P&L, 181 not operational full year.",
        "Variable costs: food, variable labor (excl manager salary), bonus, payroll taxes, workers' comp, mileage/delivery, advertising, royalty, operating supplies.",
        "Fixed costs: phone/utilities, rent, repairs/maintenance, professional fees, equipment/computer, other taxes, insurance (excl workers' comp), manager salary, misc.",
        "EBITDA = Royalty Sales - Variable Costs - Fixed Costs + Supply Chain Profit Sharing/Volume Discounts.",
        "Written substantiation available upon reasonable request."
      ]
